\end_inset

 Si
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\tau_{3}\left(r_{0}\right)=0\Rightarrow r_{0}=-\frac{l}{\sqrt{2\left|\gamma\right|}}<0\,;\,\gamma<0
\]

\end_inset

Esta solución 
\series bold
no es válida
