, por ser 
\begin_inset Formula $r_{0}$
\end_inset

 negativo.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Description
Polinomio
\begin_inset space ~
\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula $\tau_{4}=-2\sqrt{-2\gamma}r+2\left(l+1\right)$
\end_inset

 Si
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\tau_{4}\left(r_{0}\right)=0\Rightarrow r_{0}=\frac{l+1}{\sqrt{2\left|\gamma\right|}}>0\,;\,\gamma<0
\]

\end_inset

Además:
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
